Gainesville & Gulf Ry. Co., Plaintiff in Error, v. Pepper Publishing & Printing Co., Defendant in Error. F. M. Simonton, for Plaintiff in Error. *544Circuit Court of Alachua County; J. T. Wills, Judge. January 8, 1910.

Judgment in favor of defendant in error.

Writ of error dismissed before the clerk on praecipe of counsel for plaintiff in error,
